## What Each Assertion Validates

Every request validates the full semantic conversion chain:

```
Input:   POST /sales/orders/create/salesforce
         │
         ├── [SDIA] Domain = sales          ✓
         ├── [SDIA] Entity = orders         ✓
         ├── [SDIA] Action: create → c      ✓  (normalization proven)
         ├── [SDIA] Target = salesforce     ✓
         ├── [SDIA] Interface ID present    ✓  (gdcrorderscsalesforceid01)
         ├── [SDIA] Generated URL present   ✓  (https://cpi-host/http/gdcr/...)
         ├── [SDIA] KVM source = redis-k8s  ✓  (metadata-driven proven)
         ├── [SDIA] Protocol present        ✓  (http/soap)
         └── [SDIA] Version 1.0.0          ✓
```

